## ğŸš€ Getting Started  

### Prerequisites  
- Node.js (v16+)  
- MongoDB Atlas (or local setup)  
- Yarn / npm  

### Installation  

1. **Clone the repo**  
```bash  
git clone  https://github.com/Akshayaa139/MERN-ChatAI.git 
cd PingMe  


2.Install Dependencies

cd frontend-starter && npm install  
cd backend && npm install  

3. Set up environment variables
Create .env in /backend:

env
MONGO_URI=your_mongodb_connection_string  
JWT_SECRET=your_jwt_secret_key  
PORT=5000  


4. Run the app

# Start server  
cd backend && npm start  

# Start client  
cd frontend-starter && npm start  

